data.eml:eml: Two new Salamanders of the genus Onychodactylus from Eastern Honshu, Japan (Amphibia, Caudata, Hynobiidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yoshikawa, Natsuhiko, Matsui, Masafumi (2014): Two new Salamanders of the genus Onychodactylus from Eastern Honshu, Japan (Amphibia, Caudata, Hynobiidae). Zootaxa 3866 (1): 53-78, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3866.1.3
